original_title: Culinary Art Food Expo at BMICH
original_body_lines: 'Cafe 2023', the Culinary Art Food Expo International Processed Food and Hospitality Exhibition, was launched today at the Bandaranaike Memorial International Conference Hall (BMICH). The exhibition will be held until Sunday (11) from 11.00 am to 7.00 pm. Pix by Kithsiri de Mel
